Name: Average time from 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' to 'SW-Checklist Completed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Total time for 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and the end of the case

Name: Average time between 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Minimum time to complete 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' grouped by 'performer'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and the end of case grouped by the last value of performer

Name: Time until 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' for manuscripts that require 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and the end of case where activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed occurs

Name: Average waiting time to 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' after 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion'

Name: Total resolution time of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' in the process of review
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time from 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' to 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Average time it takes 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' before 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' occurs
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Total time from 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' to 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' in successful review processes (ending in 'SW-EIC Accept')
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and the end of the case

Name: Time of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' in relation to the total time of the review process
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and the end of the case

Name: 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' Cycle Time in relation to 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' impact on review process duration
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Total time for 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' in variants leading to major revisions ('SW-EIC Major Revision')
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and the end of case where activity 'SW-EIC Major Revision occurs

Name: Average time from 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' to the next activity in the most frequent process variant
Metric: The average of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time it takes 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' to be done before 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1' is sent
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1'

Name: Total time it takes 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' after 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' in the longest process variant
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion'
